### Login Flow (All Users)

[Enter College Email] вҶ’ [Send OTP] вҶ’ [Verify OTP] вҶ’ [Set Password] вҶ’ [Profile Setup] вҶ’ [Role Detection] вҶ’ [Home]

text

### CR / LR Profile Fields:
| Field | Input Type | Options |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| Name | Text | Free text |
| Roll Number | Text | Free text (validated) |
| Mobile Number | Text | Validated against DB (not OTP) |
| Branch | Horizontal scroll carousel | CAC, CE, EC, EEE, ME, CSE, IT, etc. |
| Year | Horizontal selector | 1, 2, 3, 4 |
| Semester | Auto-toggle | SEM1 / SEM2 (based on year) |
| Section | Dropdown | A вҶ’ K |

### Student Profile Fields:
| Field | Input Type |
|-------|-----------|
| Name | Text |
| Roll Number | Text |
| Mobile Number | Text |

### Role Detection Logic (After Profile Save):

User submits profile
вҶ’ Does ClassGroup exist for (branch + year + sem + section)?
вҶ’ YES: Is CR role already filled?
вҶ’ YES: Is this roll in the range? вҶ’ YES: STUDENT вҶ’ Home
вҶ’ NO CR yet: вҶ’ CR role вҶ’ RollRangeSetup
вҶ’ NO ClassGroup: вҶ’ CR role вҶ’ RollRangeSetup

