## 6. рҹ§  Core Concept: Roll Number System

> The backbone of Attenza. Everything revolves around roll numbers.

- CR enters `start_roll` and `end_roll`
- System auto-generates all rolls between them
- Only these rolls are valid across the entire app
- Every student auto-links to class via their roll number

### Validation:

roll outside range вҶ’ вқҢ "Roll number exceeds class limit"

text

### Auto-Assignment:

Student logs in with roll "25BFA04145"
CR defined range: 131вҖ“198
145 is in range вҶ’ Student auto-linked вҶ’ sees all attendance

text

### Edge Case вҖ” Student Before CR:

No ClassGroup found вҶ’ "Your CR has not set up the class. Contact your CR."
Student stays logged in (empty state)
CR creates class later вҶ’ auto-sync вҶ’ student linked automatically

text

