## 21. вҡ пёҸ Constraints & Validations

| Rule | Detail |
|------|--------|
| Roll range is final | Cannot change without admin |
| No roll outside range | Hard block + error message |
| One CR per class | DB constraint |
| One LR per class | DB constraint |
| Duplicate attendance session | UNIQUE(class_id + subject_id + date + batch) |
| Student edits only name | All other fields locked |
| Role transfer requires acceptance | Old role not revoked until accepted |
| New subjects require online | Cannot create subjects offline |
| Share screen auto-closes | 5s countdown, edit only within window |

